column5: Hi, I thought this was a good time to post my presents and ask a few questions since it it my birthday today! I went to Le Baron's this weekend and picked up a few things for steelheading. I was aloud to get quite a few things since it was my birthday and i got into enriched math. Heres a few pics: I am just wondering if this is a good start and if i should add anything to it. Thanks, Tibbs
happy birthday and enjoy your presents
Wow!! You're all set....that's some sweet stuff you got there!!!  Happy birthday by the way!
Happy birthday and congrats on getting into enriched math.  Go out and christen your new gear
Happy Birthday, some nice equipment you got there.  Now go fishing  Joey
that is one happy birthday!  Good stuff -- looks like you are ready to rock
NICELY DONE!!! READ THAT BOOK COVER TO COVER AND YOU'LL HAVE MUCH BETTTER UNDERSTAND OF TROUT AND HABITS!!! JIM DEFINATLEY KNOWS HIS STUFF!!!!
Congrats!  Dang, i wish birthday comes more than once every year.
you might wanna add a few flies and  maybe some coloured yarns....but all in all looks great.....good luck
THAT BOOK IS THE BIBLE.......I READ IT ATLEAST 3 TIMES IN THE PAST COUPLE YEARS...Jim is the man !!!
Thanks Guys!  I'll start reading the book tonight!
HAPPY BIRTHDAY!    nice gear, have fun with it!
